-- Levitt Says Robert Diamond to Blame for Libor Scandal (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2012-07-05T13:36:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-05/levitt-says-robert-diamond-to-blame-for-libor-scandal-audio-.html
Arthur Levitt , former chairman of the
U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission and senior adviser to 
Goldman Sachs, says Robert Diamond, former chief executive 
officer of Barclays Plc, is culpable for the firm's improper 
manipulation of the Libor interest rate. Levitt talks with 
Bloomberg's Ken Prewitt and Tom Keene on Bloomberg Radio's 
"Bloomberg Surveillance."   (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 05:30
 